    "description": "天羽失落，妖王再临，原本温顺的灵兽也变得异常狂暴，持续了数百年和平的神州大陆再次陷入危机之中。<br>这是一款带有Roguelite和弹幕元素的时间生存游戏。你需要在敌人源源不断地攻势下生存下来，利用战斗中积累的灵铢，提升修行者的能力，并探索这个世界的秘密，发现更多新的地图并寻找传中的秘宝。<br>      死亡并非终结，在”轮回之羽”的力量下，修行者会获得重生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2>🔸多角色选择！你可以尝试使用不同的角色，获得更多不同的体验！<br><br>🔸种类繁多且极具特色的中式Q版怪物。<br>🔸简单爽快的战斗系统，超级容易上手。<br>🔸多种武器法宝任意搭配，构筑不同的生存玩法。<br>🔸各种强大的boss等着你来挑战！<br><br>🔸歡迎玩家加入我們的QQ群：<strong>700376290</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/cabf497dda5e1d9d5dcbcbd2f562e27a.poster.avif?t=1674191111\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/cabf497dda5e1d9d5dcbcbd2f562e27a.webm?t=1674191111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/cabf497dda5e1d9d5dcbcbd2f562e27a.mp4?t=1674191111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/6a655a1e8adabb0f6d125da9c5d497bb.poster.avif?t=1674191111\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/6a655a1e8adabb0f6d125da9c5d497bb.webm?t=1674191111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/6a655a1e8adabb0f6d125da9c5d497bb.mp4?t=1674191111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171270/extras/b0084483313769833456e24bae374d0c.poster.avif?t=1674191111\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171